{
  "stem": "10353.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the heat was really on by that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Arrow Cross were going around looking for Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whoever they caught suspecting to be a Jew, because many Jews were hiding, they took them up to their headquarters.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after furious and-- and the brutal beatings, to be beyond recognition at times, at night, they took them out to this same market, [INAUDIBLE], and they-- they shot them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, my commanding officer was arrested.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know what to do here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We are alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I-- I phoned headquarters and I told them that my commanding officer was arrested and they didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After several days, the commanding officer returned and he was terribly, terribly upset.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He grew a beard, I remember he looked god awful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he-- under his breath, he told me, he says, he gave me a feminine name, because I was the-- I was doing all the housework.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He gave me a feminine name but he called me under his breath, he says Suzy-- he called me Suzy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He says, take your few things and run and run as far as you can because they are going to deport everybody.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took my things and I started to run.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where do you run?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they said-- You still had the false papers that he had given you?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it-- it didn't mean very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said there is a-- a place, a temple that is apparently protected by the Red Cross for Romanian citizens.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So somehow I got myself in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was there a few days, a couple of days, two, three days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I heard that you can also get some protection papers from the Swiss embassy, that the Swiss embassy is issuing citizenship papers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I made my way to the Swiss embassy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And although it was-- it was guarded by the Arrow Cross and also by the gendarmes, because the way Budapest is built, it can easily be cut off from either side of the street, because it's more or less built in squares.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I made my way through and I slipped into the Swiss embassy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I got into the Swiss embassy, there was a Dr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Somogyi there who knew me from before, and I knew him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I begged him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I says, please take me in, because by that time, there was already an accumulation of people in the Swiss embassy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He says, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Go upstairs and try to find yourself a little place, a corner where you can-- you can be.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was there overnight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the following day, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Dr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Somogyi came and he gave me one of those Swiss citizenship papers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He says, here is this paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know how much help it will be, but I'm sorry to tell you that you have to go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You are not allowed to stay here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But what happened, if you ran out from the Swiss embassy, the Arrow Cross and the gendarmes were standing there and they rounded you up right away.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They took you away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I had to get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was ordered to get out, so I got out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And lo and behold, they did round us up and they formed a column of certain-- I don't remember how many, about 60, 80 people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they put us in rows of 5.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I managed to get to the edge of the-- of the-- of my row.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And as we were marching, marching, marching-- and they were going around with the-- with their rifles, you know, and their bayonets against us to see that nobody gets out of line.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But as we came to one intersection, I managed to tear away and to separate and I started running.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So where do I run now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they said that there is one company, such a brigade that was left in Budapest for the purpose to clean up after the air raids.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they're primary composed of people from my home town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I got myself in after some lengthy going and walking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got in there and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I got in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I asked them that they should take me into the company.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they couldn't do it officially.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So after a couple of days, in the meantime, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was hiding out in a cellar during the night and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] tried to work that I should be taken into this company.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So finally after two days, I understand that they bribed one of the officers and they took me in.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
